WELCOME


 


Lapides
Asset Management LLC� is an independent, SEC-registered investment manager
offering value-oriented portfolios of smaller capitalization equities. Lapides
is a single strategy firm employing a fundamental, research-intensive process.
We offer four discrete concentrated products: a portfolio of micro cap
companies, a portfolio of small cap companies and a portfolio of small/mid cap
holdings, along with a highly concentrated portfolio of companies covering the
full spectrum of smaller capitalizations.
The firm's
investment products are offered to institutional investors, family offices and
high net worth individuals through commingled investment vehicles and separate
accounts. Our clients and their advisors are our partners in this enterprise.
Lapides’ objective is to consistently generate superior absolute performance
with less-than-market volatility over the long term.
This
website is intended to provide an overview of our firm. Please do not
hesitate to contact
us should you have further questions or would like
additional information.

